|{{sortname|Brian|Lawrence |nolink=1}}
|While never actually reaching the execution phase of the plan, Lawrence communicated with his collaborators via a code written in "invisible ink" hidden in [[sudoku]] puzzles. Officers grew suspicious and eventually discovered the code after a message "more heat less light" was found. The escape attempt was planned during the [[Isle of Wight Festival]] where it was thought it would arouse less suspicion.<ref>{{cite web |date= June 25, 2010|url = http://www.iwcp.co.uk/news/news/prison-break-foiled-by-sharp-officers-33431.aspx|title = Prison break foiled by sharp officers |publisher = [[Iwcp]]| accessdate = | last= |quote=}}</ref>

