|Yves Denis<br />Denis Lefebvre<br />Serge Pomerleau
|Three detainees awaiting trial for murder successfully escaped from a Quebec City prison at around 7:45&nbsp;p.m. ET.  The three detainees were identified as Yves Denis, 35, Denis Lefebvre, 53, and Serge Pomerleau, 49.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/quebec-police-search-for-3-inmates-after-helicopter-jailbreak-1.2668653 | location=Quebec | work=CBC News | first=CBC | last=News | title=Quebec police search for 3 inmates after helicopter jailbreak | date=June 7, 2014}}</ref>  The three men were arrested a couple weeks later and returned to the same facility from which they previously escaped.<ref>{{cite web|title=Escapees in Canadian Helicopter Jailbreak Captured|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/22/world/americas/canada-helicopter-jailbreak/}}</ref>

